    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>This staff is capable of launching flurries of @Localize[PF2E.TraitCold] elemental energy. It has a bespoke critical specialization effect.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Specialization Effect</strong> If the target of the critical hit is adjacent to a surface, it gets stuck to that surface by ice. The target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.eIcWbB5o3pP6OIMe]{Immobilized} and must spend an Interact action to attempt a @Check[athletics|dc:10] check to break loose from the ice; it can’t move from its space until it succeeds. The creature doesn’t become stuck if it is incorporeal, is on fire (such as a fire elemental), or could otherwise escape without effort.</p>"
    },
